  "page": "Roland",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Roland</b> is a Westerosi given name. It may refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Roland_I_Arryn\" title=\"Roland I Arryn\">Roland I Arryn</a>, the fourth King of Mountain and Vale</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Roland_II_Arryn\" title=\"Roland II Arryn\">Roland II Arryn</a>, King of Mountain and Vale, the great-grandson of Roland I</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Roland_Blackwood\" title=\"Roland Blackwood\">Roland Blackwood</a>, a nobleman of House Blackwood</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Roland_Crakehall_(Kingsguard)\" title=\"Roland Crakehall (Kingsguard)\">Roland Crakehall</a>, a knight of the Kingsguard</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Roland_Crakehall_(lord)\" title=\"Roland Crakehall (lord)\">Roland Crakehall</a>, Lord of Crakehall during the War of the Five Kings</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Roland_Darry\" title=\"Roland Darry\">Roland Darry</a>, Lord of Darry at the end of the Dance of the Dragons</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Roland_of_the_Horn\" title=\"Roland of the Horn\">Roland of the Horn</a>, a legendary knight of the Reach</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Roland_Waynwood\" title=\"Roland Waynwood\">Roland Waynwood</a>, a knight and grandson of Lady Anya Waynwood</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Roland_Westerling\" title=\"Roland Westerling\">Roland Westerling</a>, Lord of the Crag and regent to King Aegon III Targaryen</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rolland\" title=\"Rolland\">Rolland</a></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404223715\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCP